  "text": "There are many factors affecting urban compactness and productivity. According to the research from G. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , we choose several important factors, including industrial output per capita (indusp), the ratio of urban built-up area to urban area ratio (area1), the area of urban built-up (area2) and employment density (dens). The original data can be obtained from Urban Statistical Yearbook of China (volume 2000 China (volume -2013 . These variables can be calculated easily.",
